        </p>

        <div class="ai-skincare-guide__expandable-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
          <div class="ai-skincare-guide__benefits-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
            <h4 class="ai-skincare-guide__benefits-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">Key Benefits</h4>
            <ul class="ai-skincare-guide__benefits-list-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
